{
	"_circus_stage_defeat": {
		"steps": [
			{
				"type": "effect",
				"effect": {
					"type": "full_heal"
				}
			},
			{
				"type": "text",
				"text": "You come to on the sawdust floor. A blank mask looks down at you.\n\n\"A valiant effort from our challenger, but no dice!\" the Ringmaster says. \"We do hope you enjoyed the show.\"\n\nYou retreat from the stage..."
			}
		]
	},
	"_circus_stage_victory": {
		"steps": [
			{
				"type": "set_var",
				"vars": {
					"stage_fights": 1
				}
			},
			{
				"type": "effect",
				"effect": {
					"type": "full_heal"
				}
			},
			{
				"type": "text",
				"text": "The crowd erupts. The Ringmaster's voice cuts through the applause: \"It seems our challenger has triumphed this time! Will they be so lucky when they return?\""
			}
		]
	},
	"circus_enter": {
		"repeatable": false,
		"steps": [
			{
				"type": "text",
				"text": "You push through the entrance flap and step into another world.\n\nLanterns hang in clusters from every post. Performers weave between clusters of onlookers — a fire-breather, a contortionist, a man swallowing a sword with practiced boredom. The smells of popcorn and animal musk compete for dominance."
			},
			{
				"type": "enter_town",
				"town": "Gilded Hollow Circus"
			}
		]
	},
	"circus_exit": {
		"repeatable": false,
		"steps": [
			{
				"type": "set_backdrop",
				"backdrop": "sundown_circus.png"
			},
			{
				"type": "text",
				"text": "You find the entrance flap. Through the canvas, the plateau air reaches you — cold and still.\n\nSomething steps in front of it."
			},
			{
				"type": "text",
				"text": "The figure is tall, dressed in a tailcoat the colour of deep red wine. A white mask with a carved smile. A top hat, slightly askew. He holds a scepter loosely in one hand.\n\nYou didn't see him arrive."
			},
			{
				"type": "text",
				"text": "The Ringmaster tilts his head. When he speaks, his voice fills the tent without being raised.\n\n\"Already? The show has only just begun.\""
			},
			{
				"type": "text",
				"text": "You move toward the flap.\n\nSomething shifts between you and the exit. The Ringmaster stands there — still, unhurried — scepter raised across the gap like a bar across a cage.\n\n\"Our guests don't leave until the show is over.\" He tilts his head. \"And the show is never over.\""
			},
			{
				"type": "combat",
				"enemy": "Ringmaster",
				"on_victory": [
					{
						"type": "text",
						"text": "The Ringmaster watches you from behind the mask for a long moment.\n\nThen, with a single precise movement, he steps aside.\n\n\"More trouble than you're worth.\" Something in his voice sounds almost amused. \"Go, then. The show will go on without you.\"",
						"clear": true
					}
				]
			}
		]
	},
	"circus_luck_defeat": {
		"repeatable": true,
		"steps": [
			{
				"type": "random",
				"outcomes": [
					{
						"weight": 1,
						"steps": [
							{
								"type": "text",
								"text": "They sweep the coins off the counter.\n\n\"Too bad.\" The mask grins. \"Looks like you just weren't lucky enough.\"",
								"clear": true,
								"no_continue": true
							}
						]
					},
					{
						"weight": 1,
						"steps": [
							{
								"type": "text",
								"text": "\"Ohhh, so close.\" They watch the result, unmoved. \"The dice decide, not me. Blame the dice.\"",
								"clear": true,
								"no_continue": true
							}
						]
					},
					{
						"weight": 1,
						"steps": [
							{
								"type": "text",
								"text": "They lean over the counter. \"Bad luck. Pure bad luck.\" A beat. \"Come back and try again.\" They do not sound sincere, and don't bother pretending otherwise.",
								"clear": true,
								"no_continue": true
							}
						]
					},
					{
						"weight": 1,
						"steps": [
							{
								"type": "text",
								"text": "\"The crowd gives you a solid...\" They tilt a hand side to side. \"Meeeh. Better luck next time. Maybe.\"",
								"clear": true,
								"no_continue": true
							}
						]
					},
					{
						"weight": 1,
						"steps": [
							{
								"type": "text",
								"text": "They pocket the coins without ceremony. \"Play more. Get Better. Come back. Lose again. That's the whole pitch, really.\"",
								"clear": true,
								"no_continue": true
							}
						]
					}
				]
			},
			{
				"type": "set_var",
				"vars": {
					"circus_minigame_losses": {
						"add": 1
					},
					"circus_luck_losses": {
						"add": 1
					}
				}
			},
			{
				"type": "event",
				"event": "circus_luck_replay"
			}
		]
	},
	"circus_luck_replay": {
		"repeatable": true,
		"steps": [
			{
				"type": "random",
				"outcomes": [
					{
						"weight": 1,
						"steps": [
							{
								"type": "text",
								"text": "They slap the counter. \"Rematch! One hundred gold, right now, I won't even make you wait!\"",
								"clear": false,
								"no_continue": true
							}
						]
					},
					{
						"weight": 1,
						"steps": [
							{
								"type": "text",
								"text": "\"Another game?\" They're already rearranging the dice. \"Hundred gold. Quick as you like.\"",
								"clear": false,
								"no_continue": true
							}
						]
					},
					{
						"weight": 1,
						"steps": [
							{
								"type": "text",
								"text": "They stare at you. \"...Go again? Hundred gold. Yes or no.\"",
								"clear": false,
								"no_continue": true
							}
						]
					}
				]
			},
			{
				"type": "event",
				"event": "circus_minigame_replay"
			}
		]
	},
	"circus_luck_victory": {
		"repeatable": true,
		"steps": [
			{
				"type": "random",
				"outcomes": [
					{
						"weight": 1,
						"steps": [
							{
								"type": "text",
								"text": "\"Well.\" They stare at the dice. \"Well. Look at that.\" They sweep the coins across the counter toward you. \"I don't do that often. Enjoy it while it lasts.\"",
								"clear": true,
								"no_continue": true
							}
						]
					},
					{
						"weight": 1,
						"steps": [
							{
								"type": "text",
								"text": "They say nothing for a long moment. Then clap. Once. \"Okay. Fine. You win. Take your coins.\"",
								"clear": true,
								"no_continue": true
							}
						]
					},
					{
						"weight": 1,
						"steps": [
							{
								"type": "text",
								"text": "\"Extraordinary!\" They bounce on the spot in an almost forced movement. \"Good job! Good job!\"",
								"clear": true,
								"no_continue": true
							}
						]
					},
					{
						"weight": 1,
						"steps": [
							{
								"type": "text",
								"text": "They pull the coins back toward you with two fingers, slowly. \"...I'm going to need a minute.\"",
								"clear": true,
								"no_continue": true
							}
						]
					},
					{
						"weight": 1,
						"steps": [
							{
								"type": "text",
								"text": "\"Fair and square!\" They spread their hands. \"Can't argue with it. Take your reward — this time.\"",
								"clear": true,
								"no_continue": true
							}
						]
					}
				]
			},
			{
				"type": "set_var",
				"vars": {
					"circus_luck_wins": {
						"add": 1
					}
				}
			},
			{
				"type": "event",
				"event": "circus_minigame_victory"
			},
			{
				"type": "event",
				"event": "circus_luck_replay"
			}
		]
	},
	"circus_mirrors": {
		"steps": [
			{
				"type": "text",
				"text": "The House of Mirrors stands before you, as if taunting. You get a strange feeling as you stand at the entrance.",
				"no_wait": true
			},
			{
				"type": "choice",
				"header": "What do you do?",
				"choices": [
					{
						"choice": "Enter",
						"key": "fight"
					},
					{
						"choice": "Leave",
						"key": "leave",
						"type": "back"
					}
				],
				"branches": {
					"fight": [
						{
							"type": "set_backdrop",
							"backdrop": "circus_mirror2.png"
						},
						{
							"type": "text",
							"text": "The tent is full of mirrors. Every one shows you looking back — except one, which shows something else entirely.",
							"no_wait": true
						},
						{
							"type": "text",
							"text": "The masked reflection steps forward, brandishing a knife.\n\nYou mirror it and prepare to fight!"
						},
						{
							"type": "combat",
							"enemy": "Doppelganger",
							"on_victory": [
								{
									"type": "effect",
									"effect": {
										"type": "full_heal"
									}
								},
								{
									"type": "text",
									"text": "The mirror shatters. The others show only empty glass now.\n\n...\n\nCreeped out, you leave the house of mirrors."
								},
								{
									"type": "mark_used",
									"event": "circus_mirrors_fight"
								}
							],
							"on_defeat": [
								{
									"type": "set_backdrop",
									"backdrop": "circus_mirror_out.png"
								},
								{
									"type": "effect",
									"effect": {
										"type": "full_heal"
									}
								},
								{
									"type": "text",
									"text": "You come to on the floor, just outside the house of mirrors.\n\n...\n\n...That was creepy."
								}
							]
						}
					],
					"leave": []
				}
			}
		]
	},
